  "text": "In the non-linear case, the data points were weighted according to [CITATION_1] . The center c was set to zero, and the distance metric D was set to DI d , where I d is the d-dimensional identity matrix. For testing, the errors for each test point were multiplied with the same weight function used for training. ",
